name: title
title: Title
description: The main title of the Dataset

name: subtitle
title: Subtitle
description: A secondary title that amplifies or states certain limitations on the main title

name: alternativeTitle
title: Alternative Title
description: Either 1) a title commonly used to refer to the Dataset or 2) an abbreviation of the main title

name: alternativeURL
title: Alternative URL
description: Another URL where one can view or access the data in the Dataset, e.g. a project or personal webpage

name: otherId
title: Other Identifier
description: Another unique identifier for the Dataset (e.g. producer's or another repository's identifier)

name: otherIdAgency
title: Agency
description: The name of the agency that generated the other identifier

name: otherIdValue
title: Identifier
description: Another identifier uniquely identifies the Dataset

name: author
title: Author
description: The entity, e.g. a person or organization, that created the Dataset

name: authorName
title: Name
description: The name of the author, such as the person's name or the name of an organization
watermark: 1) Family Name, Given Name or 2) Organization XYZ

name: authorAffiliation
title: Affiliation
description: The name of the entity affiliated with the author, e.g. an organization's name

name: authorIdentifierScheme
title: Identifier Type
description: The type of identifier that uniquely identifies the author (e.g. ORCID, ISNI)

name: authorIdentifier
title: Identifier
description: Uniquely identifies the author when paired with an identifier type

name: datasetContact
title: Point of Contact
description: The entity, e.g. a person or organization, that users of the Dataset can contact with questions

name: datasetContactName
title: Name
description: The name of the point of contact, e.g. the person's name or the name of an organization

name: datasetContactAffiliation
title: Affiliation
description: The name of the entity affiliated with the point of contact, e.g. an organization's name

name: datasetContactEmail
title: E-mail
description: The point of contact's email address

name: dsDescription
title: Description
description: A summary describing the purpose, nature, and scope of the Dataset

name: dsDescriptionValue
title: Text
description: A summary describing the purpose, nature, and scope of the Dataset

name: dsDescriptionDate
title: Date
description: The date when the description was added to the Dataset. If the Dataset contains more than one description, e.g. the data producer supplied one description and the data repository supplied another, this date is used to distinguish between the descriptions

name: subject
title: Subject
description: The area of study relevant to the Dataset

name: keyword
title: Keyword
description: A key term that describes an important aspect of the Dataset and information about any controlled vocabulary used

name: keywordValue
title: Term
description: A key term that describes important aspects of the Dataset

name: keywordVocabulary
title: Controlled Vocabulary Name
description: The controlled vocabulary used for the keyword term (e.g. LCSH, MeSH)

name: keywordVocabularyURI
title: Controlled Vocabulary URL
description: The URL where one can access information about the term's controlled vocabulary

name: topicClassification
title: Topic Classification
description: Indicates a broad, important topic or subject that the Dataset covers and information about any controlled vocabulary used

name: topicClassValue
title: Term
description: A topic or subject term

name: topicClassVocab
title: Controlled Vocabulary Name
description: The controlled vocabulary used for the keyword term (e.g. LCSH, MeSH)

name: topicClassVocabURI
title: Controlled Vocabulary URL
description: The URL where one can access information about the term's controlled vocabulary

name: publication
title: Related Publication
description: The article or report that uses the data in the Dataset. The full list of related publications will be displayed on the metadata tab

name: publicationCitation
title: Citation
description: The full bibliographic citation for the related publication

name: publicationIDType
title: Identifier Type
description: The type of identifier that uniquely identifies a related publication

name: publicationIDNumber
title: Identifier
description: The identifier for a related publication

name: publicationURL
title: URL
description: The URL form of the identifier entered in the Identifier field, e.g. the DOI URL if a DOI was entered in the Identifier field. Used to display what was entered in the ID Type and ID Number fields as a link. If what was entered in the Identifier field has no URL form, the URL of the publication webpage is used, e.g. a journal article webpage

name: notesText
title: Notes
description: Additional information about the Dataset

name: language
title: Language
description: A language that the Dataset's files is written in

name: producer
title: Producer
description: The entity, such a person or organization, managing the finances or other administrative processes involved in the creation of the Dataset

name: producerName
title: Name
description: The name of the entity, e.g. the person's name or the name of an organization

name: producerAffiliation
title: Affiliation
description: The name of the entity affiliated with the producer, e.g. an organization's name

name: producerAbbreviation
title: Abbreviated Name
description: The producer's abbreviated name (e.g. IQSS, ICPSR)

name: producerURL
title: URL
description: The URL of the producer's website

name: producerLogoURL
title: Logo URL
description: The URL of the producer's logo

name: productionDate
title: Production Date
description: The date when the data were produced (not distributed, published, or archived)

name: productionPlace
title: Production Location
description: The location where the data and any related materials were produced or collected

name: contributor
title: Contributor
description: The entity, such as a person or organization, responsible for collecting, managing, or otherwise contributing to the development of the Dataset

name: contributorType
title: Type
description: Indicates the type of contribution made to the dataset

name: contributorName
title: Name
description: The name of the contributor, e.g. the person's name or the name of an organization

name: grantNumber
title: Funding Information
description: Information about the Dataset's financial support

name: grantNumberAgency
title: Agency
description: The agency that provided financial support for the Dataset

name: grantNumberValue
title: Identifier
description: The grant identifier or contract identifier of the agency that provided financial support for the Dataset

name: distributor
title: Distributor
description: The entity, such as a person or organization, designated to generate copies of the Dataset, including any editions or revisions

name: distributorName
title: Name
description: The name of the entity, e.g. the person's name or the name of an organization

name: distributorAffiliation
title: Affiliation
description: The name of the entity affiliated with the distributor, e.g. an organization's name

name: distributorAbbreviation
title: Abbreviated Name
description: The distributor's abbreviated name (e.g. IQSS, ICPSR)

name: distributorURL
title: URL
description: The URL of the distributor's webpage

name: distributorLogoURL
title: Logo URL
description: The URL of the distributor's logo image, used to show the image on the Dataset's page

name: distributionDate
title: Distribution Date
description: The date when the Dataset was made available for distribution/presentation

name: depositor
title: Depositor
description: The entity, such as a person or organization, that deposited the Dataset in the repository

name: dateOfDeposit
title: Deposit Date
description: The date when the Dataset was deposited into the repository

name: timePeriodCovered
title: Time Period
description: The time period that the data refer to. Also known as span. This is the time period covered by the data, not the dates of coding, collecting data, or making documents machine-readable

name: timePeriodCoveredStart
title: Start Date
description: The start date of the time period that the data refer to

name: timePeriodCoveredEnd
title: End Date
description: The end date of the time period that the data refer to

name: dateOfCollection
title: Date of Collection
description: The dates when the data were collected or generated

name: dateOfCollectionStart
title: Start Date
description: The date when the data collection started

name: dateOfCollectionEnd
title: End Date
description: The date when the data collection ended

name: kindOfData
title: Data Type
description: The type of data included in the files (e.g. survey data, clinical data, or machine-readable text)

name: series
title: Series
description: Information about the dataset series to which the Dataset belong

name: seriesName
title: Name
description: The name of the dataset series

name: seriesInformation
title: Information
description: Can include 1) a history of the series and 2) a summary of features that apply to the series

name: software
title: Software
description: Information about the software used to generate the Dataset

name: softwareName
title: Name
description: The name of software used to generate the Dataset

name: softwareVersion
title: Version
description: The version of the software used to generate the Dataset, e.g. 4.11

name: relatedMaterial
title: Related Material
description: Information, such as a persistent ID or citation, about the material related to the Dataset, such as appendices or sampling information available outside of the Dataset

name: relatedDatasets
title: Related Dataset
description: Information, such as a persistent ID or citation, about a related dataset, such as previous research on the Dataset's subject

name: otherReferences
title: Other Reference
description: Information, such as a persistent ID or citation, about another type of resource that provides background or supporting material to the Dataset

name: dataSources
title: Data Source
description: Information, such as a persistent ID or citation, about sources of the Dataset (e.g. a book, article, serial, or machine-readable data file)

name: originOfSources
title: Origin of Historical Sources
description: For historical sources, the origin and any rules followed in establishing them as sources

name: characteristicOfSources
title: Characteristic of Sources
description: Characteristics not already noted elsewhere

name: accessToSources
title: Documentation and Access to Sources
description: 1) Methods or procedures for accessing data sources and 2) any special permissions needed for access
